## When to use

- When optional input is desired that allows for multiple selections from a small list.
- As a boolean choice for a single option, either Yes or No.

## Note

- Checkboxes should not presume a selection. Select a default on page load *only* to reflect previously stated preferences.
- A checkbox should not be used to change state (such as, *Make Official*) when it is not something that can be reversed.

## Variations

### Checkbox group (default)

{{/markdown}}

<figure class="ksdg-Figure">
  <a class="ksdg-Figure-link" href="https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/347558/4036527/b4c53d14-2c9a-11e4-981e-33c531811d21.png">
