  <figcaption class="ksdg-Figure-caption">

{{#markdown}}

- A Checkbox Toggle is used to indicate whether a presented option is desired.
- Only one option is made available to the user (such as *Send email update*).
- Checkbox Toggles may be required as a way to acknowledge critical information.
- Use as a boolean choice for a single option, for example indicating to use a delivery address as a billing address.

